{"tid":43063,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（人土木去澳洲旅行車環島","createTime":"2016-12-17T08:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T14:24:15.000Z","uid":66903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3020a3970335d162a6098211d1a27ea6cd551abf","tid":43063,"uid":66903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:12:35.000Z","msg":"請問各位巴絲打，有無試過去澳洲自己駕車？有得住宿嘅車嗰隻。<br />\n有無人識點租旅行車？旅行車有無營地可以搭電攞水之類？<br />\n去澳洲有無咩要注意？<br />\n成個澳洲有無咩地方一定要去？<br />\n初步預11月至1月去澳洲，襯嗰邊天氣熱，可以玩水睇靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：無去過澳洲，乜膠野都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff04a49224ebaf6bf3cad3cb57b3a8875a0d277","tid":43063,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T21:06:29.000Z","msg":"環島？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都係預一個景點去自駕算啦，遠離市區地大人少驚你悶，係揸4,5個鐘都仲係田嗰啲<br />\n<br />\nbtw我係幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573a6759291fe6f835cf4dd80b8a2de5ff45c614","tid":43063,"uid":25622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T04:53:59.000Z","msg":"Tasmania 環島咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ac115b4b6e2ce4f2d88f164d72158cbdd01df4","tid":43063,"uid":66903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:34:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>環島？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都係預一個景點去自駕算啦，遠離市區地大人少驚你悶，係揸4,5個鐘都仲係田嗰啲<br />\n<br />\nbtw我係幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係想去澳洲郊區，因為想上山下海睇風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\